},{"localized_name":"scheduler_config","name":"scheduler_config","shape":7,"type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"scheduler_config"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"precision_config (optional)","name":"precision_config (optional)","shape":7,"type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"precision_config (optional)"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"prequant_weights (optional)","name":"prequant_weights (optional)","shape":7,"type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"prequant_weights (optional)"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"fused_mod","name":"fused_mod","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"fused_mod"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"manual_unload_model","name":"manual_unload_model","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"manual_unload_model"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"pipeline","name":"pipeline","type":"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE","links":[5]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"QuantFuncModelLoader"},"widgets_values":["/path/to/base_model/or/diffuser_model","path/to/transformer.safetensors","lighting",0,"",""," "," ",false,false]},{"id":17,"type":"QuantFuncExport","pos":[1923.6302116840586,2824.572323853623],"size":[371.5488033760116,158.4014053901451],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"pipeline","name":"pipeline","type":"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE","link":10},{"localized_name":"export_path","name":"export_path","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"export_path"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"export_mode","name":"export_mode","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"export_mode"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"export_transformer","name":"export_transformer","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"export_transformer"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"export_text_encoder","name":"export_text_encoder","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"export_text_encoder"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"export_vision_encoder","name":"export_vision_encoder","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"export_vision_encoder"},"link":null}],"outputs":[],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"QuantFuncExport"},"widgets_values":["path/to/export","all",false,false,false]},{"id":14,"type":"Note","pos":[1014.0941614475529,3044.1584386681616],"size":[547.4186683071963,392.27686828015834],"flags":{},"order":2,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"使用前阅","properties":{},"widgets_values":["本工作流专用于导出所需的量化模型，包括量化后的 Text Encoder、Vision Encoder 和 Transformer，避免每次运行时重复量化，节省时间，同时方便用户分享和传播自己的模型。使用前需配置以下参数：\n\n@Export 节点：可按需选择要导出的模型组件。若 export_mode 选择 all，则忽略下方单独选项，并将 VAE、Scheduler 等信息一并导出，确保模型下次可直接加载。\n\n@model_dir：diffusers 格式的模型路径。\n\n@transformer_path：若使用 lighting 模型，此项留空；若使用 svdq 模型，需填入预量化 Transformer 权重路径，例如 path/to/transformer/qwen-image-2511-50x-above-lighting-4steps.safetensors。\n\n@model_backend：必须与当前 Transformer 的模型类型严格对应，可选值为 svdq 或 lighting。\n\n@precision_config（仅 lighting）：需额外指定精度配置文件路径，用于逐层设定精度，具体填写方式请参考官网。\n\n#LoRA 使用说明#\n\n@lighting 模式下使用 LoRA 时，无需添加任何 Config 节点，lighting 会直接将 LoRA 权重与模型权重相加融合。\n\n@svdq 模式下使用 LoRA 时，必须添加 LoRA Config 节点，用于控制新 LoRA 与 svdq 中已有 LoRA 的组合方式。推荐使用 ROP 算法——这是我们的创新算法，可先找到多个 LoRA 之间通用的 rank，再以能量损失最小为目标进行截断。"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653","shape":"round"},{"id":15,"type":"Note","pos":[1602.7433497515751,3046.0137020199013],"size":[589.7298020307538,387.71435439733017],"flags":{},"order":1,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Readme","properties":{},"widgets_values":["This workflow is designed for exporting quantized models, including the quantized Text Encoder, Vision Encoder, and Transformer. This avoids re-quantizing on every run, saves time, and makes it easy to share your models with others. The following parameters must be configured:\n\n@Export Node: Select the model components to export as needed. If export_mode is set to all, all individual options below are ignored, and VAE, Scheduler, and other components are exported together to ensure the model can be loaded directly next time.\nmodel_dir: Path to the model in diffusers format.\n\n@transformer_path: Leave empty if using a lighting model. If using svdq, provide the path to the pre-quantized Transformer weight file, e.g. path/to/transformer/qwen-image-2511-50x-above-lighting-4steps.safetensors.\n\n@model_backend: Must strictly match the model type of the Transformer being used. Valid options are svdq or lighting.\n\n@precision_config (lighting only): An additional precision config file path is required to specify the precision of each layer. Please refer to the official documentation for details.\n\n#LoRA Usage Notes#\n\n@In lighting mode, no Config node is needed. Lighting directly merges LoRA weights into the model weights by addition.\n\n@In svdq mode, a LoRA Config node must be attached to control how the new LoRA combines with the existing LoRA inside svdq. We recommend using the ROP algorithm — our proprietary innovation that first identifies the shared rank across multiple LoRAs, then truncates based on minimum energy loss."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653","shape":"round"}],"links":[[4,9,0,5,0,"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE"],[5,10,0,6,0,"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE"],[6,6,0,7,0,"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE"],[7,5,0,8,0,"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE"],[10,7,0,17,0,"QUANTFUNC_PIPELINE"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[871.9783427771202,1422.7235143159871,315.1740505509151,321.883150488547],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[871.9783427771202,1422.7235143159871,315.1740505509151,321.883150488547],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[871.9783427771202,1422.7235143159871,315.1740505509151,321.883150488547],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":4,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[871.9783427771202,1422.7235143159871,315.1740505509151,321.883150488547],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":5,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[871.9783427771202,1422.7235143159871,315.1740505509151,321.883150488547],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":6,"title":"Lora config for svdq","bounding":[285.65998678928514,1232.902437257649,898.3380942072477,175.5039474712637],"color":"#a1309b","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":7,"title":"Lora config for svdq","bounding":[1009.6733396358168,2793.7393445032626,884.4849661039559,188.0291479973498],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":8,"title":"Lora config for svdq","bounding":[285.65998678928514,1232.902437257649,898.3380942072477,175.5039474712637],"color":"#a1309b","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":9,"title":"Lora config for lighting","bounding":[1925.1936602517396,2463.332880595377,315.88835718949485,315.23195599802057],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"workflowRendererVersion":"LG","ds":{"scale":0.6407408655869336,"offset":[-268.387723450085,-1996.7535224963708]}},"version":0.4}